# 27. Remove Element

## ğŸ” Intuition
- Remove all occurrences of a given value
- Order of elements does not matter

---

## ğŸ§  Approach (Two Pointers)
- `i` scans array
- `k` stores valid elements
- Overwrite elements not equal to `val`

---
## â± Complexity
Time: O(n) ,
Space: O(1)

## âœ… Python Code

```python
class Solution:
    def removeElement(self, nums, val):
        k = 0
        for i in range(len(nums)):
            if nums[i] != val:
                nums[k] = nums[i]
                k += 1
        return k
